<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Biotech Expansion - Mammalia</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
      <mods>
        <li>ATH's style Draconic</li>
      </mods>
      <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
        <success>Always</success>
        <operations>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/CultureDef[defName="TMM_Draconic"]/label</xpath>
            <value>
              <label>드래곤주의</label>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/CultureDef[defName="TMM_Draconic"]/description</xpath>
            <value>
              <description>신화 속 이질적인 인간들이 이끄는 드래곤의 문화입니다.</description>
            </value>
          </li>
        </operations>
      </match>
    </match>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Stoneborn - Dwarven Style Pack</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
      <mods>
        <li>Det's Xenotypes - Stoneborn</li>
        <li>Big and Small - Races</li>
      </mods>
      <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
        <success>Always</success>
        <operations>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/CultureDef[defName="TMM_Dwarven"]/label</xpath>
            <value>
              <label>드워프주의</label>
            </value>
          </li>
          <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
            <success>Always</success>
            <xpath>/Defs/CultureDef[defName="TMM_Dwarven"]/description</xpath>
            <value>
              <description>키 작은 이들로부터 이어진 드워프주의 체제입니다.</description>
            </value>
          </li>
        </operations>
      </match>
    </match>
  </Operation>
</Patch>